NOTE ON DATA:
The oil spill incident data (oils_data.csv) used in the research papers associated
with this code is the property of the National Oil Spill Detection and Response
Agency (NOSDRA), Abuja, Nigeria. The data is NOT included in this repository and
is NOT covered by this licence. Researchers must request data access directly from
NOSDRA through official channels.
